title: Palm Oil Processing Plant
description: Establish a modern palm oil processing facility to serve the growing agricultural sector in Papua New Guinea.
requirements: Minimum investment of $2.5M, proven agricultural experience, commitment to sustainable practices
benefits: Tax incentives for first 5 years, guaranteed palm fruit supply contracts, export facilitation support

title: Tourism Resort Development
description: Develop an eco-friendly resort in one of Papua New Guinea's pristine coastal locations.
requirements: Tourism industry experience, environmental compliance, minimum $5M investment
benefits: Land lease arrangements, tourism promotion support, fast-track permits

title: Mining Equipment Manufacturing
description: Establish a facility for manufacturing and maintaining mining equipment locally.
requirements: Manufacturing experience, technical expertise, quality certifications
benefits: Import duty exemptions, skilled worker training programs, government contracts

title: Renewable Energy Solar Farm
description: Develop a large-scale solar energy project to support Papua New Guinea's growing energy needs.
requirements: Renewable energy experience, grid connection capability, environmental clearances
benefits: Power purchase agreements, carbon credit opportunities, grid access guarantees

title: Seafood Processing Facility
description: Modern seafood processing and export facility leveraging Papua New Guinea's rich marine resources.
requirements: Food processing experience, export market access, HACCP certification
benefits: Fishing quota allocations, export license facilitation, cold storage subsidies
